364
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:13,910
If that's true,

365
00:21:14,210 --> 00:21:18,360
my daughter, Yuan Ying, would be your distant grandmother.

366
00:21:18,550 --> 00:21:20,140
Exactly.

367
