380
00:21:54,340 --> 00:21:56,470
Jinchuan has only one rule of conduct.

381
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,200
Pay the debts.

382
00:21:58,670 --> 00:21:59,770
A life for a life.

383
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:03,730
Distant grandfather.

384
00:22:03,730 --> 00:22:04,590
Lord Jinchuan,

385
00:22:06,320 --> 00:22:07,820
Danchuan suffered a sudden flood

386
00:22:07,820 --> 00:22:08,940
