437
00:24:38,430 --> 00:24:40,730
This has nothing to do with my brother.

438
00:24:41,150 --> 00:24:42,610
It's mainly because of me.

439
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:43,750
Distant grandmother,

440
00:24:43,750 --> 00:24:44,640
