479
00:26:07,560 --> 00:26:08,710
She still has to get married in the end.

480
00:26:08,710 --> 00:26:10,110
How dare you be stubborn?

481
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:14,380
Xu is right.

482
00:26:15,040 --> 00:26:16,900
It's time for Ying to get married.

483
00:26:17,360 --> 00:26:20,160
